2011-09-09T07:28:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/billionton-syste-august-sales-fall-79-25-table-6172-tt.html
BILLIONTON SYSTE said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 79.25% to NT$5,698,000 from NT$27,459,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales             5,698            27,459    
YOY%             -79.25%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            208,279          396,389    
YOY%             -47.46% 
=================================================================
 